I’m telling y’all I saw something very similar about 2 years back. Unexplainable UFO. Thought it was plane flying low at first but nope. Suburban. In open field. 12-2am abouts. Was very in awe in the moment. How it moved across the sky, increasing altitude unbelievably quickly. Slight spinning. Those multi colored circular lights. Looked like disc. Kinda has the ability to break like a car but in the sky.

So the mechanics of these UFOs are all the same. The one I saw moved very similarly to one in video but the lights and shape was different. There are different kinds of these ships/remote controlled devices. Just like we have different types of cars lol. With different purposes. 

Generally speaking I don’t believe in aliens or that beings from another galaxy are with us or watching us. Idk what I saw but I’m to realistic to fantasize about something that’s just speculation and has accumulated soo many baseless theories. Kinda like my own baseless fantasized theory.
